Data
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Owner
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the owner has been set
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should return the stored owner address
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the owner has been renounced (zero address)
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should return the zero address
в””в”Ђв”Ђ RequireOwner
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the owner
    в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should not revert
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the owner
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}

Transfer
в””в”Ђв”Ђ TransferOwnership
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the owner
    в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should update the owner to the new address
    в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should emit an {OwnershipTransferred} event
    в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the new owner is the zero address
    в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should set owner to zero (renounce)
    в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the new owner is the current owner (self)
    в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should leave owner unchanged
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the owner
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}

Renounce
в””в”Ђв”Ђ RenounceOwnership
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the owner
    в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should set the owner to the zero address
    в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should emit an {OwnershipTransferred} event
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the owner
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}

TwoSteps
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Data
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ PendingOwner
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when a pending owner has been set
в”‚       в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should return the pending owner address
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ when no pending owner has been set
в”‚           в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should return the zero address
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Transfer
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ TransferOwnership
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the owner
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should set pendingOwner to the new address
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should emit an {OwnershipTransferStarted} event
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should leave the current owner unchanged until acceptance
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when a pending transfer already exists
в”‚   в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should overwrite pendingOwner and emit {OwnershipTransferStarted}
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the owner
в”‚   в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ AcceptOwnership
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the pending owner
в”‚       в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should set the owner to the pending owner
в”‚       в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should clear the pending owner to zero
в”‚       в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should emit an {OwnershipTransferred} event
в”‚       в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the pending owner
в”‚       в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ when no transfer is pending
в”‚           в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}
в””в”Ђв”Ђ Renounce
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ RenounceOwnership
        в”њв”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is the owner
        в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should set the owner to the zero address
        в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ it should clear the pending owner to zero
        в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should emit an {OwnershipTransferred} event
        в””в”Ђв”Ђ when the caller is not the owner
            в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should revert with {OwnerUnauthorizedAccount}

ExportSelectors
в””в”Ђв”Ђ for each Owner facet (data, transfer, renounce, two-steps)
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ it should return an abi.encodePacked list of that facet's external function selectors in the expected order
